Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔茲米 我們就要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.34,0:00:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔茲米你得回去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.94,0:00:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.66,0:00:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們三個人是一起的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是已經有了新的夥伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.18,0:00:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能總是和我們撒嬌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別了 塔茲米
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.78,0:00:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有來世的話 我們再見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.86,0:00:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.70,0:00:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.06,0:00:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要留下我…一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.46,0:00:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是個讓人難過的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:00:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼在這兒睡著了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.06,0:01:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貌似從今天起塔茲米就是我的部下了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天然呆上司出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.66,0:01:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.42,0:01:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼鏡 眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
